		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Sounds like keyboard ghosting. I guess it could be solved by allowing remapping of keys manually so you can map them to a combination of keys that does not cause ghosting on your particular keyboard.<br /><br />A solution for the player is to use a gamepad or mechanical keyboard with NKEY rollover.

		

